  <brief_title>Reference Values for Pulse Induced Continuous Cardiac Output (PiCCO) Variables in Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>Reference Values for Cardiac Output and Blood Volume Variables in Children With Normal Cardiac Function Measured Under General Anesthesia.</official_title>
